## Troubleshooting

### HubSpot Tracking Not Working
- Check browser console for errors
- Verify Script component in `app/layout.tsx`
- Ensure `strategy="afterInteractive"` is set
- Check HubSpot portal for tracking events

### Styles Not Applying
- Remember: Tailwind v4 uses `@theme` in globals.css, not tailwind.config.ts
- Check globals.css for color variable definitions
- Use DevTools to inspect applied classes

### Domain Routing Issues
- Check `next.config.ts` rewrites configuration
- Verify Vercel domain settings
- Check DNS propagation (can take 24-48 hours)

